name: CHAROMO.TEZ Hi! 8Bit
description:
Charm UFO flew to CETO World to steal something. And something QWAYU caught was the message "Hi," a short PEPA (human) greeting.

The ancients said that this CHAROMO is suitable for people who can't speak well. If you hold QWAYU, people will talk to you. Say hi all day and all night. LOL (Tip: Practice speaking multiple languages. because there may be foreigners DM to you)

Welcome to my world : https://twitter.com/CETO_World
